data.description: Brand New Roof just completed on 7-14-2023. New heat and air system 2021. Come see this updated, easy living home. Lots of natural light and a easy flow floor plan. Close to town, yet the large beautiful property your heart desires. Enjoy your evenings on the wrap around deck while the dogs and young children stay safe in the fully fenced Back/side yard. There's also a "She Shed" to encourage your creative side and a large metal Carport to keep all your toys clean. As if that's not enough this home has Solar! Ask to see the amazing True-Up.
